msgid "Combined AWaRe profile: overall antibiotic exposure is within the reference range; AWaRe Access-group exposure is below the reference range; AWaRe Watch-group exposure is within the reference range; AWaRe Reserve-group exposure is above the reference range. Across AWaRe categories, the profile follows an escalation gradient from Access towards Reserve, indicating a shift to broader-spectrum or last-resort use. Read this together with resistance and pathogen detection results, as both Watch- and Reserve-group use may be expected to increase where resistant or multidrug-resistant pathogens are common or confirmed by microbiological diagnostics.\n"
